Dandapat Debashish is a 10-year-old child suffering from blood cancer. He belongs to a very poor family. His father is not in this world anymore, his mother looks after him. Just like Covid changed our lives, Debashish’s life was also changed. In the month of December 2021, Debashish was found covid positive. Even after he was declared negative, he was facing a lot of problems like fever, weight loss, difficulty breathing. That is why he was again admitted to hospital. Where his bone marrow test took place and he was found positive for blood cancer. Slowly, cancer spread into his chest as well. 

Blood cancer is a very harmful disease which needs chemotherapy. Until now, 20 lakh rupees has been spent on his treatment and Mrs. Mala (Debashish’s mother) cannot afford his treatment further. Now for the treatment of Debashish, 12.5 lakh is needed. It’s a humble request to all of you from the Team Dream Girl Foundation to please donate for his treatment. We really need your help.
#donation #peopleinneed #fightcancer #yourdonationmatters #ngo #ngoindia #dreamgirlfoundation #cancer #bloodcancer #togetherwecanmakeadifference
